        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2">A Motion-Point</text> that we add for you to a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">sketch-path</text> (open or closed) when you add a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Motion-Path FB</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The motion-values at the input to the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Motion-Path FB</text> control the motion of the <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Motion-Point</text> along the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">sketch-path</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Applications</text>: Robot-Path, Chains/Belts, Scissor-Lifts, Ram-R and Ram-P Dyads</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddFBMotionPath">Add Motion-Path FB</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Sketch-Loop">sketch-loop</link>.</para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">Compare with <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Motion-Driven-Part" styleclass="Interface">Motion-Part</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
